cui_name: Malignant tumor of anterior wall of nasopharynx
reasoning: Nasopharyngeal cancer subtype by anatomical wall location. Anterior wall is relatively uncommon (~12% of NPC). Global NPC incidence ~1.0 per 100k; anterior wall estimate ~0.12 per 100k. Based on GLOBOCAN 2005 NPC data with anatomical distribution from clinical registries.
source: GLOBOCAN 2005 (IARC); anatomical distribution from nasopharyngeal cancer registries
